two_of_the_nations_most_affected_by_the_tsunami , india_and_sr . lanka , are_leading_cricket-playing_nations .
the_international_cricket_council_has_launched_the_world_cricket_tsunami appeal_to_raise_funds_for_the_humanitarian_effort .
